snippet.title: Steel Rats™ Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Tate Multimedia have revealed gameplay of their upcoming motorbike combat game ‘Steel Rats™’ for the first time ever. This gameplay reveal trailer shows off the explosive, diesel-soaked world of Steel Rats™ and the stunt based, motorbike combat that fuels it. 

For more information visit: 
http://steelratsgame.com
https://facebook.com/SteelRatsGame
http://tatemultimedia.com

TRAILER CREDITS: 
Created by: Tate Multimedia
Concept: Tate Multimedia
Animation: Aleksander Kowal
VFX: Łukasz Bieńko
Edit: Aleksander Kowal, Łukasz Bieńko 
Music by: Arkadiusz Reikowski
Sound Designer & Mixer: Dawid W. Mika
